cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.AI, cs.SE

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on field robot systems and their control architecture. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper proposes a hierarchical control architecture for managing complex dynamic systems. 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is another possible category as the paper deals with cooperation among heterogeneous robots. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a formal method for modeling the hybrid systems and behavior specifications. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the design and implementation of a modular supervisor for the control architecture.
